Never was a huge Britney fan, but I recall her mental breakdown quite vividly. I remember her being constantly accosted by the paparazzi, her every move scrutinized and judged by the public. Me included. If all this is true, I could not feel more horrible for passing judgement against this poor girl. No one deserves this kind of treatment. Slavery of a different kind. I used to think she was just another media queen with everything at her disposal and not a care in the world. Makes her song ""Lucky"" all too poignant now.
